Various leaders trooped to the Nairobi residence of Vihiga Senator George Khaniri after the death of his mother Josephine Kageha Khaniri on Sunday afternoon. She was the widow of former Hamisi MP, the late Nicodemus Khaniri. Among those who went to offer their condolences were Amani National Congress party leader Musalia Mudavadi, Cord principals Raila Odinga and Moses Wetang&rsquo;ula.